#: ../../source/user_guide/backends.rst:167
msgid "SGLang"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/user_guide/backends.rst:168
msgid ""
"`SGLang <https://github.com/sgl-project/sglang>`_ has a high-performance "
"inference runtime with RadixAttention. It significantly accelerates the "
"execution of complex LLM programs by automatic KV cache reuse across "
"multiple calls. And it also supports other common techniques like continuous"
" batching and tensor parallelism."
msgstr ""
"`SGLang <https://github.com/sgl-project/sglang>`_ cuenta con un runtime de "
"inferencia de alto rendimiento basado en RadixAttention. Acelera "
"significativamente la ejecuciĂłn de programas complejos de LLM al reutilizar "
"automĂˇticamente la cachĂ© KV entre mĂşltiples llamadas. TambiĂ©n admite otras "
"tĂ©cnicas comunes de inferencia, como el procesamiento por lotes continuo y "
"el procesamiento paralelo de tensores."

#: ../../source/user_guide/backends.rst:175
msgid "MLX"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/user_guide/backends.rst:176
msgid ""
"`MLX <https://github.com/ml-explore/mlx-examples/tree/main/llms>`_ provides "
"efficient runtime to run LLM on Apple silicon. It's recommended to use for "
"Mac users when running on Apple silicon if the model has MLX format support."
msgstr ""
"`MLX <https://github.com/ml-explore/mlx-examples/tree/main/llms>`_ "
"proporciona una forma de ejecutar LLM de manera eficiente en chips Apple "
"Silicon. Cuando el modelo incluye el formato MLX, se recomienda que los "
"usuarios de Mac con chip Apple Silicon utilicen el motor MLX."
